{"tid":1676500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇黎新一年全世界都開始覺醒","createTime":"2019-10-26T13:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T13:24:46.000Z","uid":174493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bede586b1639ecba30656dc3aabad2e839307e63","tid":1676500,"uid":174493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:23:31.000Z","msg":"有理相信溝通易左，世界各地都因為見到其他地區成功而開始企出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由學習唔同地方鎮壓手法到應對，到吸收世界唔同地方集會示威手法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91eaa3f4a9ef3912a44da99e51a363b3fddc0dc0","tid":1676500,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:23:58.000Z","msg":"我真係唔想製造一個廢post, 所以我唔會開post 評論某間米線店<br />\n我直接係唔同post 屌<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我唔撚知你係五毛、風向撚定係戇鳩，但係開post 之前可唔可以用個死人腦諗下野</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係2019年10月26日，標題有「譚仔」嘅post，有超過100個，我數到100個就停撚左，因為我覺得真係好撚on9</span></span><br />\n推今晚集會post 又唔見你咁勤力？<br />\n推聽日尖沙咀集會又唔見你會咁勤力？<br />\n一間咁嘅濕鳩食肆，一間咁大間嘅食肆唔通奶共會唔知咩<br />\n洗唔洗幾百個post 一齊討論呀屌<br />\n<br />\n爭氣d 啦，唔好犀比班濕鳩五毛睇<br />\n多啲獨立思考，拒絕風向<br />\n光復香港唔係靠熱血就夠，仲要智慧架大佬<br />\n一齊努力，要班五毛無糧出"},{"pid":"f847148f22835b0fa057cfc30f80d238cae8d27b","tid":1676500,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:24:44.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"717eb73780b678ae04cee63a21cbc2e07eeeecce","tid":1676500,"uid":274538,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DuAco4p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDuAco4p.jpg&h=37e157b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4cE4ZCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2